text: Zack T. Young was an American football player and coach. He served as the head football coach at Louisiana Tech University in 1906, compiling a record of 2–1–3. Prior to coaching, Young was a starting quarterback for his alma mater. ==Head coaching record== ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:American football quarterbacks Category:Louisiana Tech Bulldogs football coaches Category:Louisiana Tech Bulldogs football players
